\q2 \w and|strong="H8179"\w* beat their breasts \add to show that they are very sad\add*.   
\q1
\v 8  \add The people will rush from\add* \w Nineveh|strong="H5324"\w*  
\q2 \w like|strong="H5927"\w* [SIM] water rushes \w from|strong="H5921"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* broken dam.  
\q1 \add The officials\add* \w will|strong="H3824"\w* \w shout|strong="H6963"\w*, “Stop! Stop!”  
\q2 \w but|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* people \w will|strong="H3824"\w* \w not|strong="H5927"\w* \w even|strong="H5921"\w* look \w back|strong="H5927"\w* \add as they run away\add*.   
\q1
\v 9  \add The enemy attackers say to each other,\add* “Seize \w the|strong="H3117"\w* silver!  
\q2 Grab \w the|strong="H3117"\w* gold!  
\q1 \w There|strong="H1992"\w* \w is|strong="H1931"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* huge amount \w of|strong="H3117"\w* \w very|strong="H1992"\w* valuable \w things|strong="H1992"\w* \w in|strong="H3117"\w* \w this|strong="H1931"\w* \w city|strong="H1931"\w*,  
\q2 more valuable \w things|strong="H1992"\w* than \w anyone|strong="H1931"\w* \w can|strong="H5975"\w* count!”   
\q1
\v 10  \add Soon everything valuable in the city\add* \w will|strong="H3519"\w* \w be|strong="H3701"\w* seized \w or|strong="H3701"\w* ruined.  
\q2 People \w will|strong="H3519"\w* \w be|strong="H3701"\w* trembling, \w with|strong="H3627"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* result \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w they|strong="H3605"\w* \w will|strong="H3519"\w* not \w be|strong="H3701"\w* able \w to|strong="H3701"\w* fight.  
\q2 \w Their|strong="H3605"\w* faces \w will|strong="H3519"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w become|strong="H2091"\w* pale.   
\b  
\q1
\v 11  \add After that happens, people will say,\add*  
\q1 “What happened \w to|strong="H3820"\w* [RHQ] \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \add great city of Nineveh\add*?  
\q2 \add It was like\add* [MET] \w a|strong="H3068"\w* den \add full\add* \w of|strong="H6440"\w* young lions,  
