\q1
\v 12  \add The soldiers in Nineveh were like\add* [MET] \w lions|strong="H3715"\w* \w that|strong="H1931"\w* killed \w or|strong="H1980"\w* strangled \add other animals\add*  
\q2 \add and brought the meat\add* \w to|strong="H1980"\w* \w their|strong="H8033"\w* dens.”   
\b  
\q1
\v 13 \w The|strong="H4390"\w* Commander \w of|strong="H4390"\w* \w the|strong="H4390"\w* armies \w of|strong="H4390"\w* angels says \add to the people of Nineveh\add*,  
\q1 “\w I|strong="H1767"\w* am opposed \w to|strong="H1767"\w* \w you|strong="H1767"\w*;  
\q2 \w I|strong="H1767"\w* will cause \w your|strong="H4390"\w* chariots \w to|strong="H1767"\w* \add be burned in fires and\add* go up \w in|strong="H2963"\w* smoke.  
\q1 \w Your|strong="H4390"\w* \w young|strong="H3833"\w* men will be \w killed|strong="H2614"\w* \w with|strong="H4390"\w* swords.  
\q2 \add Your soldiers\add* will never again conquer \add other nations\add*  
\q2 \w and|strong="H3833"\w* seize \w their|strong="H4390"\w* valuable possessions.  
\q1 \w Your|strong="H4390"\w* \w messengers|strong="H4390"\w* will never again take messages \add to other nations, demanding that their armies surrender to them\add*.”   
\c 3  
\s1 Nineveh will be punished  
\q1
\v 1 Terrible \w things|strong="H3605"\w* \w will|strong="H5892"\w* happen \w to|strong="H5892"\w* \add Nineveh\add*,  
